<div id="home-banner">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row" id="home-banner-container">
      <div class="col-5 col-xl-5">
        <%= image_tag("logo.png", :alt => "logo", :id => "img-banner-logo") %>
        <div id="home-banner-text">
          <h2 class="title-blue">Creating high performing teams</h2>
          <p class="justify-text">We believe that leaders and teams can always get better. Better Teams. Better Times. Striving for better is both healthy and something you can habituate.</p>
          <p class="justify-text">So teamup∞™ offers a range of solutions built on neuroscience designed to accelerate individual and team performance.</p>
        </div>
        <%= link_to "our solutions", root_path(@root, :anchor => "home-solutions"), id: "home-banner-btn" %>
      </div>
      <div class="col-7 col-xl-7">
        <%= video_tag "lined_head_silhouette.mp4", :type => "video/mp4", autoplay: :autoplay, preload: 'auto', muted: :muted, :height => '100%', :width => "100%", :id => "banner-video-head"%>
      </div>
      <% flash.each do |type, msg| %>
        <div class="alert alert-info">
          <%= msg %>
        </div>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- <div id="home-intro-gradient">  -->
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-6 col-xl-6" id="home-intro-pic">
        <%= image_tag("report_magazine.jpg", :alt => "reports", :id => "img-reports") %>
      </div>
      <div class="col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-6 col-xl-6 home-text-right">
        <p class="subtitles-grey"><strong>teamup∞™ are proprietary neuroscience-based assessments</strong></p>
        <h2 class="title-pink">Based on neuroscience</h2>
        <p class="justify-text">The teamup∞™ model for high performing teams is based exclusively on application of the latest neuroscience towards collaboration and collective intelligence. Workplaces are social systems, filled with people. Each and every brain is wired to be beautifully and predictably biased, energy conserving, meaning making and risk avoiding.</p>
        <p class="justify-text">So it’s essential that we use this growing knowledge to better enable teams to flourish. This is where teamup∞™ is different, because we lead with neuroscience.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="home-btn-middle">
      <%= link_to "the science", "https://drive.google.com/file/d/1SN-c73-kVXU0CGZYfPFST0_RcCsVWxWU/view", target: :_blank, class: "btn-pink"%>
    </div>
    <div class="divider"></div>
    <div class="home-text-middle">
      <p id="quote"><em>“Without data, you’re just another person with an opinion”</em></p>
      <p id="quote-author">(W. Edwards Deming)</p>
    </div>
  </div>
<!-- </div> -->

<div class="divider_two"></div>

<!-- Temporary solution to background color div home-how-color -->
<div id="home-how-color">
  <div class="container" id="home-how">
    <h2 class="title-purple">How it works</h2>
    <p>teamup∞™ suggests there are six ongoing leadership roles needed to build a high performing team. The model is an infinity loop to represent both the sequential and ongoing responsibility of leaders to create an effective team.</p>
    <p>Our assessments help you to hone in on which of the six roles you do well, which you could improve upon, along with practical suggestions you can apply to your work today.</p>
    <div id="home-how-img">
      <%#= image_tag("infinity_loop.jpg", :alt => "infinity loop model", :id => "img-infinity-loop") %>
      <%= video_tag "Loop-v5.mp4", :type => "video/mp4", autoplay: :autoplay, preload: 'auto', muted: :muted, :height => '460px', :width => "900px", :id => "home-video-loop"%>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div id="home-solutions-gray">
  <div class="container" id="home-solutions-content">
      <div id="home-solutions-title">
        <h2 class="title-green">Our Solutions</h2>
        <p class="subtitles-grey"><strong>We offer different leadership and team development solutions depending on your specific needs</strong></p>
      </div>
  </div>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <% @solutions.each_with_index do |solution, index| %>
        <div class="col-12 col-md-7 col-lg-7 col-xl-7 margin-top-50">
          <p class="subtitles-grey"><strong><%= solution.tagline %></strong></p>
          <h2 class="<%= solution.name == 'neuro-selfie™' ? 'title-blue' : 'title-green' %>"><%= solution.name %></h2>
          <p class="justify-text"><%= solution.description_one %></p>
          <p class="justify-text"><%= solution.description_two %></p>
          <div class="margin-top-50">
            <% if solution.button == 'book your neuro-selfie™' %>
              <%= link_to solution.button, new_solution_contact_path(solution), class: 'btn-blue' %>
            <% else %>
              <%= link_to solution.button, new_solution_contact_path(solution), class: 'btn-green' %>
            <% end %>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-12 col-md-5 col-lg-5 col-xl-5 home-sol-img-left image-hide">
          <!-- The iteration syntax wasn't working -->
          <% if solution.name == 'neuro-selfie™' %>
            <%= image_tag('report_ns.jpg', alt: 'report', class: 'img-report') %>
          <% elsif solution.name == 'teamup∞™ 180°' %>
            <%= image_tag('report_180.jpg', alt: 'report', class: 'img-report') %>
          <% elsif solution.name == 'teamup∞™ 360°' %>
            <%= image_tag('report_360.jpg', alt: 'report', class: 'img-report') %>
          <% elsif solution.name == 'teamup∞™ for teams' %>
            <%= image_tag('report_teams.jpg', alt: 'report', class: 'img-report') %>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>


<!-- WORKSHOP -->
